    "description": "<p>The European Free Trade Association (EFTA) plays a key role in the global and European trade. This presentation&nbsp;proposes the analysis of its past, its present and its future perspectives. After revising its origins, its foundational incentives and its legal-economic and organisational basic elements, an analysis based on current commercial indicators is performed. Finally, a discussion is proposed about the potential reincorporation of the United Kingdom to the EFTA space after Brexit&nbsp;and the main answers provided by the research are collected.</p>", 
